Package com.oracle.coherence.concurrent.locks

Class LockOwner

java.lang.Object
com.oracle.coherence.concurrent.locks.LockOwner
All Implemented Interfaces:
ExternalizableLite, PortableObject, Serializable
public class LockOwner extends Object implements ExternalizableLite, PortableObject
The identity of a lock owner, represented by the UID of the member, and the ID of a thread holding or attempting to acquire the lock.
Author:
Aleks Seovic 2021.10.19
